text: Discover your dream home in the South Hills neighborhood. This custom-built gem sits on one of the largest lots in the community and welcomes you w/a beautiful 2 story foyer, curved staircase and vaulted trey ceilings in the living and dining room. The Great Room showcases an updated kitchen with hardwood floors and expansive views of the fully fenced, private backyard. The main floor offers a versatile 5th bedroom or office space. Enjoy outdoor living on the spacious patio, with a large lawn, mature trees, and a berry garden. This home has over 3, 000 sqft w/ 5 bdrms, 3 bthrms, and a 3-car garage. W/a newer roof and HVAC system, this well-maintained home is move-in ready for you. Located just moments from Lake Padden and Galbraith Mountain.

Sun-filled rambler in the heart of Bellingham with a peaceful yard and patio to enjoy the summer. Take advantage of extra space the insulated shed provides. It would make a great gym, yoga room, woodworking shop, office, or another place to relax. The fully fenced backyard is a gardeners dream to plant flowers, fruits, and veggies. Plenty of updates have been aded such as barn doors, light fixtures, fresh paint, quartz countertops, and all new stainless steel appliances. Two living rooms on opposite sides of the house provides ample rooom for entertaining. New roof in 2021 and the exterior paint is only a few years old. Easy access to I-5, schools, Costco, restaurants, and other shopping centers. Make Home RD your new home.

Welcome to this beautifully enhanced single level, 3-bedroom, 1.75-bath home on a spacious corner lot in a very well-established Ferndale neighborhood. At nearly 2000 square feet, this open space A/C infused rambler boasts brand new siding, interior/exterior paint, furnace and floors throughout. Additional upgrades also include new gutters, trim/baseboard, fridge, and washer/dryer. All of the heavy lifting has been completed with over $50k in recent updates. Take advantage of your fully fenced backyard and firepit to host your BBQs and fun filled gatherings. The oversized 160 square foot shed/shop is perfect for additional storage, and it'll fulfill any gardening wishes. Complete with a two-car garage, there's nothing else you'll need!

This architect-designed South Hill home offers bright & exceptional living spaces w/ stunning views of Bellingham Bay! Excellent floor plan includes primary suite & all main living areas on the main level. Lower level includes family room, 2 bedrms, bthrm & bonus room for work, hobby or storage space. Enjoy views from both levels! Kitchen updated in 2020 along w/ other updates around the house. Furnace & water heater new in 2020. Home boasts many skylights, fireplace, 2 decks, hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings & garage w/ .5 bthrm. Spacious, partially covered deck is perfect for enjoying amazing sunsets. Low maintenance yard space. There's parking space for a small RV or use it for extra parking. Located on a very quiet & private street!

As you walk into this dreamland, you will fall in love with the oasis yard and pool area. The waterfall jacuzzi and BBQ area top off this fully-fenced backyard making the perfect place for making memories. Recently remodeled chef's kitchen feat. quartz counters. Don't miss the colorful sunsets from the upper floor media room. Spacious master suite with 5 piece bath and walk-in closet. Grand entry with gorgeous staircase. Brand new carpet throughout. Additional features include fresh paint, double staircases, office on the main, built-in cabinets in office and family room, hardwood floors, 3 car garage, new LED lighting throughout. Close to walking, biking and hiking trails, Padden & Galbraith, downtown shopping and restaurants.

Architecturally exciting, contemporary 3 bed. home on coveted west side w/ sweeping water & island westerly views! This gorgeous home offers everything in one package; sustainability, luxury & access to the water & outer islands just one block from home (professionally installed mooring buoy to convey with sale). A plethora of very recent upgrades include; all windows ('23), siding('23), commercial-grade carpet ('23), Swedish firebox ('23), solar panel installation ('23), heat-pump &mini-splits throughout home ('23), new roof ('21). This home has nearly zero cost energy-wise with the solar electric connected to the heating systems. Automatic generator w/dedicated propane tanks. Plus, one car garage with workshop + addl' storage building.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District

text: Discover the charm of Blaine in this beautifully maintained corner lot home, built in 2012, featuring fresh paint and new carpets. Providing a wonderful floor plan, this property includes a large primary bedroom conveniently located on the main floor. The kitchen flows seamlessly into the dining and living areas, perfect for entertaining. Upstairs, find sizable bedrooms accompanied by a full bath. Enjoy the privacy of a fully fenced backyard - ideal for gardening enthusiasts or pets. Situated near schools, downtown amenities, the bay, and with easy access to I-5. Better yet, no HOA!

Charming vintage Craftsman home lovingly preserved with it's timeless period finishes including unique fir floors, mouldings & light fixtures. Relax in open living & dining room with new wood-burning fireplace(heats the whole house) and custom tilework made in Michigan. Remodeled bathroom nods to the past with claw foot tub with shower head.Kitchen is charming with a new vintage Heartland stove and colorful marmoleum floor.Front bedroom has a walk-in closet that could be converted into ensuite bathroom. Detached 2 car garage has additional 264 square feet of finished space with heat and A/C-currently office & work out room.10 year old roof.New electrical panel.2018 furnace.Laundry in basement but could be located on back covered porch.

Desirable Silver Beach living on this beautiful, large corner lot on a dead end street! Enjoy one level living in this large 4 bedroom/2.5 bathroom home. Located in an ideal location with close proximity to Lake Whatcom, Barkley Village and incredible trails, but, all the while you will feel like you are in your own private park. Enjoy the gorgeous sunsets from your front deck or gardening in the backyard. This home has plenty of natural light as you flow throughout the large living room, dining room and kitchen with large eating area. Have fun entertaining guests on the large deck in the backyard. You cant beat the tranquility of this adorable neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to call this place home!

This charming home features a cozy yet modern ambiance, boasting a single bedroom and bathroom. Built in 2024, it offers the allure of newness, promising pristine conditions and contemporary design elements throughout. The kitchen is adorned with sleek stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher, ensuring efficiency and style in meal preparation and cleanup. Additionally, the convenience of in-unit laundry hookups adds further practicality to daily living. Nestled within a tranquil park-like environment, this residence provides a serene retreat from the bustle of city life. Its proximity to the freeway enhances accessibility to nearby amenities and destinations, ideal blend of convenience and tranquility for discerning homeowners.

Welcome to Stonecrest, perfectly situated near King Mtn, Irongate, Bellis Fair & the Bay to Baker Trail. Dont miss this meticulously maintained home with incredible outdoor living space. The moment you walk in theres no denying the warmth & vibrancy this home offers. You will love the open concept main level layout & obvious care that this home has been given. The cozy gas fireplace, granite countertops, stainless appliances, ceiling fan & half bath are all an added bonus. Upstairs, find a generous primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and ensuite. Two more bedrooms, full bath & laundry round out the second floor. Finally, step out to your private backyard oasis, featuring a cozy deck, patio, privacy fence and pergola - a true sanctuary!

Imagine coming home by driving through a low-traffic street to arrive at your cul-de-sac destination. Park in the 2 car garage with extra storage, and walk into a lovely 3 bedroom turn-key home with fresh paint. As you prepare dinner in the large kitchen with an island and nook, you can utilize the brand-new stove & microwave. Move into the dining room featuring vaulted ceilings! Slider off-kitchen leads to a nice covered back patio where you can look over the mature landscaping and huge yard for games and gardening. End the night with relaxation in the living room where you can enjoy the gas fireplace with spaciousness for entertaining. This neighborhood is in high demand, and next to amazing schools. Don't miss out!

Welcome to this quintessential Pacific Northwest craftsman on a quiet cul-de-sac in a well-established east-side neighborhood. Prepare to be greeted by a spacious living room with tall ceilings, a large kitchen & dining area that looks out to a fenced backyard, & a spacious covered patio, ideal for entertaining. This 2300+ home has a seamless flow & space for all, including 2 bedrooms on the main level, two bedrooms, & a bonus room upstairs. The main level primary suite offers a beautiful tiled walk-in shower & a large walk-in closet. Custom details include granite countertops, Knotty Alder solid core doors, trim & custom cabinets, an oversized garage, and a storage shed. Enjoy easy, comfortable living here.

Come see this tremendously updated, single level 2 bedroom, 2 bath condominium which has one of the finest views of the golf course and Lake Whatcom available in the sudden Valley community. This unit is light and bright, with vaulted ceilings and upper windows which create a sense of volume and openness. The kitchen has been completely updated with new cabinets, granite counter tops, and stainless steel appliances. Other features include: new trim, doors and paint throughout; updated bathrooms; new flooring and light fixtures. Enjoy the front entry deck in the morning, and the massive new deck on the view side of the unit - which offers amazing sunsets! This unit has new siding & windows and is located just a short walk to the pool.

Discover unparalleled waterfront living in this stunning, custom Bay-front estate, an architectural gem of the Pacific NW. Captivating saltwater and island views - & no powerlines - unlike any you've seen. Rare direct access to miles of beach from the backyard. Located just 4.5 miles from downtown Bellingham, 6 miles from PeaceHealth Medical Center. Luxuriate in the stunning Chef's kitchen, Spa-like Primary Suite, or any of the interior spaces & exquisite finishes of Doug Fir & artisan stonework. Multiple guest suites upstairs + a luxurious ADU your guests will absolutely LOVE, or use it as the ultimate home office with its separate entrance & garage. Radiant floor heat, brand new roof, zoned sprinklers + more. Owner Financing negotiable.

Immaculate, turn-key weekend getaway cabin! Fully furnished (down to the dishes), sleeps four with sofa bed. A writer's retreat, a place of tranquility for creativity, a place to sail, swim & hike- you've found it. Excellent investment opportunity with a two bd. septic so you can expand on this large 1/3 of an acre lot. Easy-care gorgeous no-mow native landscape & a short walk to the swimming lake, boat launch & beach, a great location! A classic style featuring a wrap-around porch, high open ceilings w/ skylights, garden window & clean lines throughout. You will be impressed by the love & care that shine through! The lower level includes a laundry room, workspace, and storage for your kayak & outdoor equipmentsimple living at its finest.

text: Shangri-la in Cornwall Park Neighborhood! This meticulously renovated, 1460 sq ft, 3 bed, 2 bath home has it all. Front includes private patio w/serene landscaping & pavers that wrap around the home. Step inside to timeless hardwood & fir, cozy living area w/gas fireplace & sun-drenched dining room. Kitchen features granite countertops, cherry cabinets, stainless appliances including farmhouse sink, tile backsplash & floors. 2 bdrms & bath on main. Large primary upstairs w/multiple closets, & huge bath suite w/ soaker tub, tiled shower & skylight. Big basement w/ W/D & tons of storage. Private oasis in fenced & hardscaped backyard that includes outdoor shower, hot tub, firepit area, storage & finished garage. Paved alley parking spot.

text: Here's your opportunity to own a townhome-style condo walkable to Fairhaven, with access to the Interurban Trail right outside your door. In addition, step outside from the primary bedroom to a lovely private patio surrounded by nature. The second bedroom can also function as an office or a media room, with a convenient built-in Murphy bed. This unit has 2 garage parking spots, plus one assigned outdoor spota rare feature!

Uncover the potential in this 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom cosmetic fixer. With a little sweat equity, you can turn this property into your dream home, relishing a low-maintenance, easy-care lifestyle in a prime location just off Portal Way with no through streets. Don't miss this opportunity to make this property your own!

Have you ever dreamed of owning a home with water and sunset views, then this home just might make your dreams come true! This home is close and walkable to the Historical Fairhaven District, granting easy access to dining, shopping. and very close to the Chuckanut Mountain trail system!

Discover this 4-bedroom farmhouse set on 33 picturesque acres, offering a perfect blend of pasture and parklike grounds. Nestled on a quiet road with stunning Mt. One of the best priced homes in Whatcom County! Cozy 1 bedroom cottage on a quiet cul de sac. Home will require some TLC but has great potential and room for your finishing touches. Private lot with shop space and shed for storage. Embrace rustic tranquility out in Maple Falls!
